replies.body:
Smite has 60s CD while exhaust has 210s. Smite can also help you secure dragon and baron, or easier lvl1 golems for your ADC.

It doesn't provide nearly as much utility in a fight, that's obvious, but I still think it could be an interesting choice for some champions. The 50% MS slow is actually very powerful.

But they're nerfing the slow to 20% in the next patch and giving you a 20% MS buff to compensate, so... I don't know about supports, but I will enjoy playing {{champion:120}}
